== 背景 ==

2015年7月20日[[2015年蘇魯奇爆炸案|苏鲁奇爆炸案]]造成33人死亡后，[[土耳其军事|土耳其軍队]]一直与[[伊斯兰国|伊斯兰国]]（ISIL）和[[库尔德工人党|库尔德工人党]]（PKK）[[库尔德人-土耳其冲突_(2015年至今)|新一轮的叛乱]]战斗。与库尔德工人党重新展开的武装冲突导致[[库尔德人-土耳其和平进程|和平进程]]终结，2012年政府与库尔德工人党就停火达成一系列和平谈判协议。随着针对库尔德人工人党和伊斯兰国的[[亞爾欽烈士行動|空袭]]，后来军事行动的目标开始明确地集中在库尔德工人党驻扎在[[伊拉克库尔德斯坦|伊拉克北部]]的武装力量，促使有关反库尔德工人党的暴力活动在以库尔德人为主的土耳其东南部激增。截止10月7日，自七月以来的暴力浪潮已导致141名士兵和1,740名武装分子死亡，以致部分亲政府的评论家表示库尔德人工人党接近乎失败。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.hurriyet.com.tr/gundem/30258824.asp|title=Terör saldırılarında 93 günlük bilanço: Bin 740 terörist öldürüldü|author=AA|date=2015-10-07|work=TÜRKİYE'NİN AÇILIŞ SAYFASI|accessdate=2016-11-06|archive-date=2015-10-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151010061110/http://www.hurriyet.com.tr/gundem/30258824.asp|dead-url=no}}</ref>然而，大量士兵的死亡也促使该国其他地区的动乱，[[土耳其民族主义|土耳其民族主义者]]攻击了人民民主党（HDP）的总部。许多政治家和评论家声称，该国已接近[[内战|内战]]。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.dw.com/tr/t%C3%BCrkiye-i%C3%A7-sava%C5%9F%C4%B1n-e%C5%9Fi%C4%9Finde/a-18702391 |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2020-09-24 |archive-date=2020-09-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200907135202/https://www.dw.com/tr/t%C3%BCrkiye-i%C3%A7-sava%C5%9F%C4%B1n-e%C5%9Fi%C4%9Finde/a-18702391 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.cumhuriyet.com.tr/haber/siyaset/295783/Demirtas___Bu_ulkede_ic_savas_cikmasina_izin_vermeyecegiz.html|title=Cumhuriyet Gazetesi – Demirtaş:  Bu ülkede iç savaş çıkmasına izin vermeyeceğiz|date=2015-06-10|publisher=cumhuriyet.com.tr|accessdate=2016-11-06|archive-date=2016-10-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161001021054/http://www.cumhuriyet.com.tr/haber/siyaset/295783/Demirtas___Bu_ulkede_ic_savas_cikmasina_izin_vermeyecegiz.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

=== 政局 ===
日益增长的暴力事件导致执政党[[正义与发展党|正义与发展党]]（AKP）在[[2015年6月土耳其大選|2015年6月大选]]中失去[[土耳其大国民议会|国会]]优势，也是13年来首次未能取得国会过半数议席。袭击发生时，[[艾哈迈德·达武特奥卢|艾哈迈德·达武特奥卢]]领导的正义与发展党政府仍在掌权，直到新的联合政府的形成，总统[[雷杰普·塔伊普·埃尔多安|雷杰普·塔伊普·埃尔多安]]2015年8月24日呼吁提前举行[[2015年11月土耳其大選|新的大选]]后，艾哈迈德·达武特奥卢于2015年8月28日上任[[2015年土耳其临时政府选举|临时当选政府]]。批评者指责正义与发展党试图从[[民族主义行动党|民族主义行动党]]（MHP）收复民族主义者的选票，而故意终结[[库尔德人-土耳其和平进程|和平进程]]，也试图通过制造动荡而减少东南部人民民主党（HDP）大本营的投票率。该地区的暴力事件引发了人们对于选举能否安全进行的担忧。

== 事件 ==

=== 察觉目标 ===
爆炸发生前不久，由土耳其进步工会联合会（DISK）、土耳其工程师和建筑师商会联盟（TMMOB）、人民民主党（HDP）、土耳其医学协会（TTB）和公共工人工会联合会（KESK）举行的“劳动、和平与民主”集会正在举行。<ref name="sozcu.com.tr1">{{cite web|url=http://www.sozcu.com.tr/2015/gundem/ankaradaki-baris-mitinginde-patlama-956103/|script-title=tr:Ankara’daki Barış Mitingi’nde patlama|date=2015-10-10|publisher=sozcu.com.tr|accessdate=2016-11-06|archive-date=2016-11-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161107011418/http://www.sozcu.com.tr/2015/gundem/ankaradaki-baris-mitinginde-patlama-956103/|dead-url=no}}</ref>集会计划于{{link-tr|衛生廣場|Sıhhiye, Ankara}}举行，火车站立交桥是集聚区。据报道，许多人民民主党（HDP）的支持者准备出席集会，集会区还有众多人民民主党、[[劳动党_(土耳其)|劳动党]]（EMEP）和[[被压迫者社会党|被压迫者社会党]]（SGDF）的旗帜。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.milliyet.com.tr/flas-ankara-tren-gari-gundem-2129787/|title=Son Dakika Haberi: Ankara'da patlama... 47 ölü iddiası – Milliyet.com.tr|date=2015-10-10|work=MЭLLЭYET HABER – TЬRKЭYE'NЭN HABER SЭTESЭ|accessdate=2016-11-06|archive-date=2019-09-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190912055916/http://www.milliyet.com.tr/gundem/son-dakika-haberi-ankarada-patlamada-son-rakam-aciklandi-2129787|dead-url=no}}</ref>

=== 爆炸 ===
第一枚炸弹在当地时间（[[欧洲东部夏令时间|EEST]]）2015年10月10日10:04爆炸，当时集会参与者正在唱纪念1969年[[血腥星期日|血腥星期日]]的赞歌。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.sozcu.com.tr/2015/gunun-icinden/ankaradaki-patlamada-aci-detay-956346/|script-title=tr:Ankara’daki patlamada acı detay!|date=2015-10-10|publisher=sozcu.com.tr|accessdate=2015-10-10|archive-date=2015-10-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151012181906/http://www.sozcu.com.tr/2015/gunun-icinden/ankaradaki-patlamada-aci-detay-956346|dead-url=no}}</ref>第二枚炸弹在几秒钟后爆炸。爆炸发生在[[国家情报组织_(土耳其)|国家情报组织]]（{{lang|en|MIT}}）总部附近。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.aktifhaber.com/ankaradaki-patlamada-korkunc-rakam-savci-52-kisi-oldu-dedi-1241892h.htm|title=Ankara'daki Patlamada Korkunç Rakam: Savcı, 52 Kişi Öldü Dedi|date=2015-10-10|work=Aktif Haber|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151011173002/http://www.aktifhaber.com/ankaradaki-patlamada-korkunc-rakam-savci-52-kisi-oldu-dedi-1241892h.htm|archivedate=2015-10-11|accessdate=2016-11-06}}</ref>爆炸发生后不久，安全部队清除了附近的第三枚和第四枚炸弹。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.milliyet.com.tr/ankara-da-3-bomba-panigi-gundem-2129828/|title=Ankara'da 3. bomba paniği|date=2015-10-10|work=MİLLİYET HABER – TÜRKİYE'NİN HABER SİTESİ|accessdate=2016-11-06|archive-date=2016-03-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305150541/http://www.milliyet.com.tr/ankara-da-3-bomba-panigi-gundem-2129828/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

=== 伤亡 ===
爆炸当天，最初死亡人数是86人，另有186人受伤。<ref name="sozcu.com.tr1"/><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.hurriyet.com.tr/gundem/30281272.asp|title=Ankara'daki patlamada ölü sayısı 86|author=Nurettin KURT/ ANKARA|date=2015-10-10|newspaper=Hürriyet|accessdate=2016-07-07|archive-date=2015-10-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151012183250/http://www.hurriyet.com.tr/gundem/30281272.asp|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.latimes.com/world/europe/la-fg-turkey-bomb-attack-20151010-story.html|title=Two bomb blasts kill 86 at peace rally in Turkish capital|author=AP Member Choice Complete|date=2015-10-10|work=[[洛杉矶时报|洛杉矶时报]]|accessdate=2015-10-10|archive-date=2015-10-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151013001714/http://www.latimes.com/world/europe/la-fg-turkey-bomb-attack-20151010-story.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>第二天，公布的死亡总数上升至97人。<ref>{{cite web|title=Ankara'da terör saldırısı: 97 ölü|url=http://www.ntv.com.tr/turkiye/ankarada-teror-saldirisi-97-olu,G7aJ87ksF0Kd8ko_oYJuOw|publisher=NTV|accessdate=2016-11-06|archive-date=2016-04-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160422224051/http://www.ntv.com.tr/turkiye/ankarada-teror-saldirisi-97-olu%2cG7aJ87ksF0Kd8ko_oYJuOw|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|script-title=tr:Ankara’daki Patlamada Ölen 97 Kişi Karanfillerle Anıldı|url=http://www.hurriyet.com.tr/yerel-haberler/antalya-haberleri/ankara-daki-patlamada-olen-97-kisi-karanfillerl_179942|publisher=自由 (土耳其媒体)|accessdate=2016-11-06|archive-date=2016-05-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160529215608/http://www.hurriyet.com.tr/yerel-haberler/antalya-haberleri/ankara-daki-patlamada-olen-97-kisi-karanfillerl_179942/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Ölü sayısı 97'ye yükseldi|url=http://www.aljazeera.com.tr/haber/olu-sayisi-97ye-yukseldi|publisher=半岛电视台土耳其语|accessdate=2016-11-06|archive-date=2017-06-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170626040310/http://www.aljazeera.com.tr/haber/olu-sayisi-97ye-yukseldi|dead-url=no}}</ref>10月14日，根据总理发表的声明，死亡人数上升至99人。<ref>{{cite web|title=Turkish PM: We lost 99 in Ankara blasts|url=http://www.aa.com.tr/en/turkey/turkish-pm-we-lost-99-in-ankara-blasts/445270|publisher=Anadolu Ajansı|accessdate=2015-10-14|language=tr|archive-date=2015-10-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151016194323/http://www.aa.com.tr/en/turkey/turkish-pm-we-lost-99-in-ankara-blasts/445270|dead-url=no}}</ref>在接下来的几天里，有人在医院里经医治无效，致死亡人数上升到100人<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.sabah.com.tr/gundem/2015/10/16/ankaradaki-saldirida-yasamini-yitirenlerin-sayisi-100e-cikti|script-title=tr:Ankara’daki saldırıda yaşamını yitirenlerin sayısı 100'e çıktı|date=2015-10-16|work=沙巴|accessdate=2016-11-06|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304083201/http://www.sabah.com.tr/gundem/2015/10/16/ankaradaki-saldirida-yasamini-yitirenlerin-sayisi-100e-cikti|dead-url=no}}</ref>至102人。<ref name="hdn102">{{cite web|title=Ankara Bombing death toll rises to 102: Chief Public Prosecutor’s Office|url=http://www.hurriyetdailynews.com/ankara-bombing-death-toll-rises-to-102-chief-public-prosecutors-office.aspx?pageID=238&nID=89988&NewsCatID=341|publisher=自由每日新闻|accessdate=2015-10-17|archive-date=2015-10-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151017115253/http://www.hurriyetdailynews.com/ankara-bombing-death-toll-rises-to-102-chief-public-prosecutors-office.aspx?pageID=238&nID=89988&NewsCatID=341|dead-url=no}}</ref>

[[土耳其医学协会|土耳其医学协会]]（{{lang|en|TTB}}）发表的报告则表示，有97人死亡，超过400人受伤，<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.sozcu.com.tr/2015/gundem/turk-tabipler-birligi-97-kisi-oldu-400-yarali-956551/|script-title=tr:Türk Tabipler Birliği: ’97 kişi öldü, 400 yaralı’|date=2015-10-10|work=sozcu.com.tr|language=Tr|accessdate=2015-10-11|archive-date=2015-10-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151012181821/http://www.sozcu.com.tr/2015/gundem/turk-tabipler-birligi-97-kisi-oldu-400-yarali-956551|dead-url=no}}</ref>后来死亡人数更新到105<ref>{{cite web|title=Ölü Sayısı 105'e Yükseldi|url=http://www.ttb.org.tr/index.php/Haberler/katliam-5640.html|publisher=[[土耳其医学协会|土耳其医学协会]]|accessdate=2015-10-11|language=tr|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170614043638/http://www.ttb.org.tr/index.php/Haberler/katliam-5640.html|archive-date=2017-06-14|dead-url=yes}}</ref>至106人<ref>{{cite web|title=Death toll 106 in suicide blasts: Ankara Chamber of Medical Doctors|url=http://www.hurriyetdailynews.com/death-toll-106-in-suicide-blasts-ankara-chamber-of-medical-doctors.aspx?pageID=238&nID=89889&NewsCatID=341|publisher=自由每日新闻|accessdate=2015-10-14|language=tr|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304081328/http://www.hurriyetdailynews.com/death-toll-106-in-suicide-blasts-ankara-chamber-of-medical-doctors.aspx?pageID=238&nID=89889&NewsCatID=341|dead-url=no}}</ref>。国际媒体说有105至106人死亡，508人受伤。<ref name=NRC29Jun16>NRC商报，2016-06-29。</ref>

亲库尔德人的[[人民民主党_(土耳其)|人民民主党]]（HDP）声称第一天死亡人数为128人，<ref>{{cite web|title=HDP kriz masası: Ankara katliamında 128 kişi yaşamını yitirdi|url=http://www.birgun.net/haber-detay/hdp-kriz-masasi-ankara-katliaminda-128-kisi-yasamini-yitirdi-91933.html|publisher=[[一天_(土耳其报纸)|一天 (土耳其报纸)]]|accessdate=2015-10-11|language=tr|archive-date=2019-01-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190105220847/https://www.birgun.net/haber-detay/hdp-kriz-masasi-ankara-katliaminda-128-kisi-yasamini-yitirdi-91933.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>但几天后撤销了声明并为此误导性声明道歉。<ref>{{cite web|title=Düzeltme ve özür|url=http://www.hdp.org.tr/basin-aciklamalari/basin/duzeltme-ve-ozur/6372|publisher=[[人民民主党_(土耳其)|HDP]]|accessdate=2015-10-13|language=tr|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304113924/http://www.hdp.org.tr/basin-aciklamalari/basin/duzeltme-ve-ozur/6372|archivedate=2016-03-04}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=HDP'den '128 kayıp' açıklaması: Hatalıyız özür dileriz|url=http://www.hurriyet.com.tr/gundem/30303059.asp|publisher=[[自由_(土耳其媒体)|自由 (土耳其媒体)]]|accessdate=2015-10-13|language=tr|archive-date=2015-10-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151014125444/http://www.hurriyet.com.tr/gundem/30303059.asp|dead-url=no}}</ref>

=== 即时反应 ===
现场的目击者告诉媒体，警方在炸弹爆炸后不久就开始使用催泪瓦斯，同时阻止救护车通过。愤怒的人们试图在爆炸后攻击警车，HDP称警方袭击将伤员运送至安全地带的人。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-34495161|title=Ankara explosions leave more than 80 dead – officials|date=2015-10-10|accessdate=2015-10-10|archive-date=2015-10-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151010164519/http://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-34495161|dead-url=no}}</ref>

爆炸后不久，卫生部长穆罕默德·米埃津奧盧（{{lang|tr|Mehmet Müezzinoğlu}}）、内政部长[[塞拉米·奥特洛|塞拉米·奥特洛]]（{{lang|tr|Selami Altınok}}）、司法部长[[凯南·伊佩克|凯南·伊佩克]]（{{lang|tr|Kenan İpek}}）到现场察看情况。然后，示威者高呼反AKP口号，兩人到场后不到一分钟被迫离开。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.sozcu.com.tr/2015/gundem/bakanlara-protesto-956364/?utm_source=segmentify&utm_campaign=scn_b804283a812d0000&utm_content=956364%7Csozcu&utm_medium=click|title=Patlama yerinde bakanlara protesto!|date=2015-10-10|publisher=sozcu.com.tr|accessdate=2016-11-06|archive-date=2015-10-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151012200757/http://www.sozcu.com.tr/2015/gundem/bakanlara-protesto-956364/?utm_source=segmentify&utm_campaign=scn_b804283a812d0000&utm_content=956364%7Csozcu&utm_medium=click|dead-url=no}}</ref>安卡拉总检察长宣布，他们正在调查两名自杀式袭击者，而[[土耳其国家铁路|土耳其国家铁路]]则表示，途径[[安卡拉中央火车站|安卡拉中央火车站]]的列车将有延误。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.takvim.com.tr/guncel/2015/10/10/3-ve-4-bomba-ihtimaline-karsi-anons|title=3. ve 4. bomba ihtimaline karşı anons|publisher=takvim.com.tr|accessdate=2016-11-06|archive-date=2016-11-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161107010815/http://www.takvim.com.tr/guncel/2015/10/10/3-ve-4-bomba-ihtimaline-karsi-anons|dead-url=no}}</ref>

总理[[艾哈迈德·达武特奥卢|艾哈迈德·达武特奥卢]]取消了所有预定活动，并表示将停止竞选活动三天。他会见了总统[[雷杰普·塔伊普·埃尔多安|雷杰普·塔伊普·埃尔多安]]，埃尔多安在事件发生后也取消了伊斯坦布尔的活动。随后总理召开安全会议，副总理[[亚尔钦·阿克多安|亚尔钦·阿克多安]]（{{lang|tr|Yalçın Akdoğan}}）、[[努曼·库尔图卢什|努曼·库尔图卢什]]（{{lang|tr|Numan Kurtulmuş}}）和[[图赫里勒·蒂尔凯什|图赫里勒·蒂尔凯什]]（{{lang|tr|Tuğrul Türkeş}}），[[国家情报组织|国家情报组织]]（MIT）副部长[[哈坎·费丹|哈坎·费丹]]（{{lang|tr|Hakan Fidan}}）、内政部长塞拉米·奥特洛、司法部长凯南·伊佩克、安卡拉市长[[穆罕默德·库德齐尔拉西|穆罕默德·库德齐尔拉西]]（{{lang|tr|Mehmet Kılıçlar}}）、安全总干事[[基拉李提·里克瑟斯|基拉李提·里克瑟斯]]（{{lang|tr|Celalettin Lekesiz}}）和其他总理府和卫生部的高级官员。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bloomberght.com/haberler/haber/1829412-ankarada-tren-garina-giden-koprunun-altinda-patlama-yaralilar-var|title=Sağlık Bakanı ölü sayısını 86 olarak açıkladı – Bloomberg HT|work=BloombergHT|accessdate=2016-11-06|archive-date=2016-11-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161107011452/http://www.bloomberght.com/haberler/haber/1829412-ankarada-tren-garina-giden-koprunun-altinda-patlama-yaralilar-var|dead-url=no}}</ref>

[[广播电视最高委员会|广播电视最高委员会]] ({{lang|tr|RTÜK}})接到[[土耳其总理|总理]]的请求后，宣布了对爆炸事件所有新闻报道的临时禁令。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.posta.com.tr/turkiye/HaberDetay/Basbakanlik-in-talebi-uzerine-yayin-yasagi-geldi.htm?ArticleID=305301|title=Başbakanlık'ın talebi üzerine yayın yasağı geldi|work=Posta|accessdate=2016-11-06|archive-date=2016-08-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160806154758/http://www.posta.com.tr/turkiye/HaberDetay/Basbakanlik-in-talebi-uzerine-yayin-yasagi-geldi.htm?ArticleID=305301|dead-url=no}}</ref>袭击后由于巨大的使用量，[[Twitter|Twitter]]和[[Facebook|Facebook]]访问速度变慢。<ref>{{Cite news|url = http://www.hurriyet.com.tr/twitter-ve-facebook-fena-yavasladi-30281716|title = ESB: Twitter ve Facebook kapatılmadı Neden yavaşladı?|date = 2015-10-11|work = Hürriyet|access-date = 2015-10-16|archive-date = 2015-10-12|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20151012183456/http://www.hurriyet.com.tr/twitter-ve-facebook-fena-yavasladi-30281716|dead-url = no}}</ref>

== 肇事者 ==

=== 初步猜测 ===
安卡拉总检察长表示，他们正在调查两起自杀式爆炸案。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.radikal.com.tr/turkiye/bassavci_iki_canli_bomba_ihtimali_uzerinde_duruyoruz-1449209|title=Başsavcı: İki canlı bomba ihtimali üzerinde duruyoruz|date=2015-10-10|work=Radikal|accessdate=2016-11-06|archive-date=2016-03-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160315164359/http://www.radikal.com.tr/turkiye/bassavci_iki_canli_bomba_ihtimali_uzerinde_duruyoruz-1449209/|dead-url=no}}</ref>爆炸发生前一天，有人看到一个匿名[[Twitter|Twitter]]账户声称，安卡拉将发生爆炸。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.sozcu.com.tr/2015/gundem/ankaradaki-bombali-saldiriyi-bir-gun-once-twitterdan-yazdi-956488/ |script-title=tr:Ankara’daki bombalı saldırıyı bir gün önce Twitter’dan yazdı! |website=sozcu.com.tr |date=2015-10-10 |accessdate=2015-10-10 |language=Tr |trans_title=(He/She) wrote Ankara bombed attack one day ago from Twitter! |archive-date=2015-10-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151012181429/http://www.sozcu.com.tr/2015/gundem/ankaradaki-bombali-saldiriyi-bir-gun-once-twitterdan-yazdi-956488 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

没有任何已知的非国家犯罪组织发表声明对袭击负责，导致对可能的袭击者的猜测。[[民族主义行动党|民族主义行动党]]（MHP）领导人德夫莱特·巴赫切利表示，袭击与七月发生[[苏鲁奇|苏鲁奇]]的[[2015年蘇魯奇爆炸案|爆炸]]相似，加重了[[伊斯兰国|伊斯兰国]]（ISIL）的嫌疑。<ref>{{cite news|url = http://www.imctv.com.tr/bahceliden-saldiri-aciklamasi/|script-title = tr:Bahçeli’den saldırı açıklaması|website = imctv.com.tr|date = 2015-10-10|accessdate = 2015-10-10|language = Tr|trans_title = Attack statement from Bahçeli|deadurl = yes|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151012220241/http://www.imctv.com.tr/bahceliden-saldiri-aciklamasi/|archivedate = 2015-10-12|df = }}</ref>据报道，炸弹的材料类型与苏鲁奇爆炸使用的相似，标识着两起事件之间存在潜在的联系。<ref name="#1">{{cite news|title=HDP co-leader slams Erdoğan, gov't for attack that claimed 86 lives|url=http://www.hurriyetdailynews.com/hdp-co-leader-slams-erdogan-govt-for-attack-that-claimed-86-lives.aspx?pageID=238&nid=89681|work=自由每日新闻|date=2015-10-10|accessdate=2016-11-06|archive-date=2016-11-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161106185413/http://www.hurriyetdailynews.com/hdp-co-leader-slams-erdogan-govt-for-attack-that-claimed-86-lives.aspx?pageID=238&nid=89681|dead-url=no}}</ref>

[[人民民主党|人民民主党]]（HDP）公开指责土耳其国家和政府引导了袭击，指责政府与[[非政府行为体|非政府行为体]]合作，以解决政府存在的不足。<ref name="#1"/>人民民主党指控执政党[[正义与发展党|正义与发展党]]（AKP）是“手上沾满鲜血的杀人犯”，也是土耳其和平与安全的头号威胁。人民民主党的指责遭到了正义与发展党政府的强烈批评。

