=== 调查 ===
最初，政府暗示行凶者可能是下列反政府组织：<ref>{{cite news|title=Ankara bombing: Who is behind Turkey's deadliest attack?|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-34504326|agency=BBC新闻|date=2015-10-12|accessdate=2016-11-06|archive-date=2016-11-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161106185618/http://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-34504326|dead-url=no}}</ref>[[伊斯兰国|伊斯兰国]]／达伊沙（IS）、库尔德工人党（PKK）、[[革命人民解放黨-陣線|革命人民解放黨-陣線]]（DHKP-C）和[[马列主义共产党_(土耳其)|马列主义共产党]]（MLKP）。

爆炸后一天，达武特奥卢暗示早期调查表明IS牵连其中。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.theguardian.com/world/2015/oct/12/turkey-blames-ankara-bombings-on-islamic-state|title=Turkey blames Islamic State for Ankara bombings|accessdate=2015-10-13|archive-date=2015-10-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151013141936/http://www.theguardian.com/world/2015/oct/12/turkey-blames-ankara-bombings-on-islamic-state|dead-url=no}}</ref>然而，反对党{{which|date=2015-10}}并不同意这一结果。<ref>{{Cite news|url = http://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-34505030|title = Turkish PM blames Ankara bombing on Islamic State|last = |first = |date = 2015-10-12|work = |access-date = 2015-10-12|via = |publisher = BBC新闻|archive-date = 2015-10-12|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20151012174147/http://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-34505030|dead-url = no}}</ref>

尤努斯·埃姆雷·阿拉戈茨，一个来自[[阿德亚曼|阿德亚曼]]的库尔德族人，他是[[2015年蘇魯奇爆炸案|苏鲁奇爆炸]]行凶者阿卜杜拉赫曼·阿拉戈茨的弟弟，政府怀疑他是自杀式袭击者之一。<ref name="telegraph11925064">{{cite web|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/europe/turkey/11925064/Ankara-bombing-Claims-emerge-that-culprit-could-be-brother-of-terrorist-involved-in-previous-atrocity.html|title=Ankara bombing: Claims emerge that culprit could be brother of terrorist involved in previous atrocity|accessdate=2015-10-14|quote=The younger Alagoz brother, of Kurdish origin born in Adiyaman, is believed to have acted on behalf of Isil. The 20-year-old is believed to have gone to Syria last year with his brother, Turkish media reported.|archive-date=2015-10-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151013234715/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/europe/turkey/11925064/Ankara-bombing-Claims-emerge-that-culprit-could-be-brother-of-terrorist-involved-in-previous-atrocity.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>10月14日，媒体报道称，尤努斯和第二名嫌疑人俄梅珥·德尼斯·丁达尔都已认为{{who|date=2015-10}}与[[ISIL|ISIL]]有关系，土耳其警察利用爆炸现场[[DNA|DNA]]识别了他们。<ref name="ibtimes">{{cite web|url=http://www.ibtimes.co.uk/yunus-emre-alagoz-brother-suruc-bomber-identified-ankara-suicide-attacker-1523973|title=Yunus Emre Alagoz: Brother of Suruc bomber 'identified' as Ankara suicide attacker|accessdate=2015-10-14|archive-date=2015-10-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151015145317/http://www.ibtimes.co.uk/yunus-emre-alagoz-brother-suruc-bomber-identified-ankara-suicide-attacker-1523973|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="hdn238">{{cite web|url=http://www.hurriyetdailynews.com/death-toll-from-ankara-attack-rises-to-99-turkish-pm-.aspx?pageID=238&nID=89892&NewsCatID=509|title=Death toll from Ankara attack rises to 99: Turkish PM|accessdate=2015-10-19|date=2015-10-15|work=自由|archive-date=2015-10-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151016121218/http://www.hurriyetdailynews.com/death-toll-from-ankara-attack-rises-to-99-turkish-pm-.aspx?pageID=238&nID=89892&NewsCatID=509|dead-url=no}}</ref>10月19日，正式认定两名自杀炸弹袭击者中的一人为尤努斯·埃姆雷·阿拉戈茨。<ref name="alagoz">{{cite web|url=http://www.hurriyetdailynews.com/ankara-suicide-bomber-officially-identified-as-brother-of-suruc-attacker.aspx?pageID=238&nID=90087&NewsCatID=341|title=Ankara suicide bomber officially identified as brother of Suruç attacker|accessdate=2015-10-19|archive-date=2015-10-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151020145540/http://www.hurriyetdailynews.com/ankara-suicide-bomber-officially-identified-as-brother-of-suruc-attacker.aspx?pageID=238&nID=90087&NewsCatID=341|dead-url=no}}</ref>

